# Three Tier Demo App

## Architecture
- React frontend (web-tier)
- Node.js/Express backend (app-tier)
- MySQL database (db)
- Nginx reverse proxy

## Run with Docker Compose
\`\`\`bash
docker-compose up -d
\`\`\`

## Access
- Web app: http://localhost
- API endpoint: http://localhost/api/message

## Development
### Web tier
\`\`\`bash
cd web-tier
npm install
npm run dev
\`\`\`

### App tier
\`\`\`bash
cd app-tier
npm install
npm start
\`\`\`
